<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q7_v15" title="Q7_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un mapa se muestra una ruta marcada formada por 6 segmentos iguales. Cada segmento de la ruta representa 7,5 km.</p>
    <p>Una persona recorre esa ruta en bicicleta en 3 días. El primer día recorre 
      <m:math display="inline">
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      de la ruta total, el segundo día recorre 
      <m:math display="inline">
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      de lo que le falta por recorrer después del primer día y el tercer día recorre el resto de la ruta.
      ¿Cuántos kilómetros recorre el tercer día?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">15<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La ruta total mide <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>7,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El primer día se recorren <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, por lo que 15 km corresponden al primer día, no al tercero. Después del primer día quedan <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km; el segundo día se recorren <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, y para el tercer día quedan <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">12<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La ruta total mide <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>7,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El primer día recorre <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, por lo que quedan <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El segundo día recorre <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, así que el tercer día recorre el resto: <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">18<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La ruta total mide <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>7,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El primer día se recorren <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, por lo que quedan 30 km. El segundo día se recorren <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, así que 18 km corresponden al segundo día, no al tercero. El resto para el tercer día es <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">3<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La ruta total mide <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>7,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. El primer día se recorren 15 km y quedan 30 km. El segundo día se recorren <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km. Entonces para el tercer día quedan <m:math display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> km, no 3 km.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular la longitud total de la ruta</strong></p>
            <p>La ruta tiene 6 segmentos iguales y cada uno representa 7,5 km.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>7,5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              km
            </p>
            <p>La ruta completa mide 45 km.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular lo recorrido el primer día</strong></p>
            <p>El primer día recorre 
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
              de la ruta total.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              km
            </p>
            <p>Después del primer día quedan:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>15</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              km
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular lo recorrido el segundo día</strong></p>
            <p>El segundo día recorre 
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
              de lo que faltaba después del primer día, es decir, de 30 km.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              km
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular lo recorrido el tercer día</strong></p>
            <p>El tercer día recorre el resto de la ruta:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math display="inline">
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>30</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>18</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              km
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La persona recorre 12 km el tercer día. La alternativa correcta es B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>